  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    Disapplication notice: school inspections legislation changes
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">Secretary of State for Education issues a seventh notice about changes to state-funded school inspections requirements during the coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak.</p>

  </div>
</div>

